text: Rick Zuijderwijk (born 13 April 2001) is a Dutch professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Willem II. ==Club career== Zuijderwijk joined the Willem II academy in 2010. He made his professional debut with Willem II in a 2–0 Eredivisie loss to SBV Vitesse on 10 August 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Breda Category:Dutch footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Willem II (football club) players Category:Eredivisie players
